e \overline{0}\;\wedge\;\overline{b}
e \overline{0}\;\Longrightarrow\;\overline{a}*\overline{b}
e \overline{0}$$ which I am not able to. I read many proofs but they either define order on $\mathbb{Z}$ which I don't want to do yet or they use cancellation law of $*$ which is equivalent to what I am trying to prove now. Thank you very much.

